WEBVTT

01:06:09.855 --> 01:06:10.397
That's the deal.

01:06:10.938 --> 01:06:12.438
We bust in and Nick's not there.

01:06:12.438 --> 01:06:13.647
Mora's not going, we're going.

01:06:14.105 --> 01:06:15.147
And he's never gonna know we're there.

01:06:15.272 --> 01:06:15.522
Cal.

01:06:15.522 --> 01:06:16.855
Team minus 17 hours, director.

01:06:23.230 --> 01:06:24.772
Keep me in the loop every step.

01:06:25.272 --> 01:06:26.730
Within two hours, I brief the presidents

01:06:26.730 --> 01:06:28.813
and prime ministers and
kings and queens of everywhere

01:06:29.438 --> 01:06:30.147
so they can prepare.

01:06:31.397 --> 01:06:32.022
Prepare for what?

01:06:32.938 --> 01:06:34.438
For the possibility of no Christmas.
